Survey 11 - What’s new?

Prepared by: UK

Last update: 2021-11-10

DEMOGRAPHICS GLOBAL SAMPLE Survey 11

  • Data presented here were collected between 2021-06-04 06:43:14 and 2021-09-21 07:06:05

  • This data were collected from 706 people.

  • Self-reported average age of participants: 44 years old.

  • Participant ages ranged from 16 to 110 years old

  • Sample is 68.1 % (N = 481) female

IMMUNIZATION PASSPORTS

The question of immunization passports has been popular already in Survey 9 and 10. We decided to inspect the answers again, this time for those who were not vaccinated and provided responses.

To what extent would the introduction of ‘immunity passports’ influence your decision to get vaccinated?

Table corresponding to the plot

1 = It would make me more likely to get vaccinated 2 = No influence 3 = Less likely to get vaccinated

Level of influence N Proportion

3 48 31.17
